# Module 10: Monitoring, Compliance, and Governance in the AWS Cloud 

## Overview
This module explains how AWS helps you **monitor resources**, **audit activity**, and **govern environments at scale**.  
You learn how monitoring, compliance, and governance build on one another to create secure, compliant, and well-managed cloud environments.

---

## Learning Objectives

| Objective | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| Monitoring Progression | Understand how monitoring leads into governance and compliance |
| Cloud Monitoring | Define monitoring in the AWS Cloud |
| Auditing | Understand why auditing activity is critical |
| Compliance | Define compliance and AWS compliance benefits |
| Governance | Learn how AWS services help manage and govern multi-account environments |

---

## Monitoring in the AWS Cloud

| Topic | Description |
|------|-------------|
| **Monitoring** | Observing systems, applications, and resources to track performance and health |
| **Purpose** | Detect issues, optimize performance, and ensure reliability |
| **Benefits** | Improves visibility, availability, and operational awareness |

---

## Amazon CloudWatch

| Item | Description |
|----|-------------|
| **Service** | Amazon CloudWatch |
| **Purpose** | Real-time monitoring of AWS resources and applications |
| **Benefits** | Visibility into metrics, logs, and alarms |
| **Use Cases** | Performance monitoring, alerting, troubleshooting |
| **Resource Link** | https://aws.amazon.com/cloudwatch/ |

---

## Auditing in AWS

| Topic | Description |
|------|-------------|
| **Auditing** | Tracking actions taken in an AWS environment |
| **Importance** | Supports security investigations, compliance, and accountability |
| **Key Question Answered** | Who did what, where, and when |

---

## AWS CloudTrail

| Item | Description |
|----|-------------|
| **Service** | AWS CloudTrail |
| **Purpose** | Records account activity and API calls |
| **Benefits** | Security monitoring, auditing, troubleshooting |
| **Events** | Logs user actions and service activity |
| **Insights** | Detects unusual or anomalous API activity |
| **Resource Link** | https://aws.amazon.com/cloudtrail/ |

---

## CloudTrail Events and Logs

| Component | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Events** | Records of API calls and user activity |
| **Logs** | Stored event data for review and investigation |
| **Insights** | Automated detection of abnormal behavior |

---

## Compliance in AWS

| Topic | Description |
|------|-------------|
| **Compliance** | Meeting regulatory and industry requirements |
| **AWS Role** | Provides compliant infrastructure and documentation |
| **Customer Role** | Ensure configurations and usage meet requirements |
| **Benefits** | Reduces risk, supports audits, improves trust |

---

## AWS Artifact

| Item | Description |
|----|-------------|
| **Service** | AWS Artifact |
| **Purpose** | Access AWS compliance and security documentation |
| **Types** | Reports & Agreements |
| **Benefits** | On-demand audit artifacts |
| **Resource Link** | https://aws.amazon.com/artifact/ |

