## AWS Organizations

| Item | Description |
|----|-------------|
| **Service** | AWS Organizations |
| **Purpose** | Central management of multiple AWS accounts |
| **Benefits** | Policy enforcement, account automation |
| **Key Concepts** | Accounts, organizational units (OUs), SCPs |
| **Resource Link** | https://aws.amazon.com/organizations/ |

