## AWS Control Tower

| Item | Description |
|----|-------------|
| **Service** | AWS Control Tower |
| **Purpose** | Governance at scale for multi-account environments |
| **Benefits** | Enforces security and compliance rules |
| **Use Cases** | Enterprise landing zones |
| **Resource Link** | https://aws.amazon.com/controltower/ |

