## IAM Access Analyzer

| Item | Description |
|----|-------------|
| **Service** | IAM Access Analyzer |
| **Purpose** | Identify overly permissive access |
| **Benefits** | Enforces least privilege |
| **Use Cases** | Security audits |
| **Resource Link** | https://aws.amazon.com/iam/features/analyze-access/ |

---

## Summary
In Module 10, you learned how AWS supports monitoring, compliance, and governance throughout the cloud lifecycle.  
You explored services that provide observability, auditing, compliance reporting, and enterprise-scale governance, helping ensure secure, compliant, and well-managed AWS environments.

